pullrequest.title: update TurtleBot3 models and add TurtleBot3 House

content.raw: A TB3 model for a standalone Gazebo tutorial will be great. I just want to double check that the two approaches won't conflict if you install both at the same time. As well that if a model evolves there's a plan to make sure that older demos keep working.
